Returns Policy
Definition: 'Return' is defined as the action of giving back the item purchased by the Buyer to the Seller on the Slrshoppee Platform. Following situations may arise:
1.	Item was defective
2.	Item was damaged during the Shipping
3.	Products was / were missing
4.	Wrong item was sent by the Seller/shop entity.
Return could also result in refund of money in most of the cases.
Points to be noted:
1.	Seller can always accept the return irrespective of the policy.
2.	If Seller disagrees a return request, Buyer can file a dispute under the Buyer Protection Program*.
We encourage the Buyer to review the listing before making the purchase decision. In case Buyer orders a wrong item, Buyer shall not be entitled to any return/refund.
Buyer needs to raise the return request within the return period applicable to the respective product.Once Buyer has raised a return request by contacting Us on Our Toll Free Number, Seller/shop entity while closing the return ticket can select one of the following:
1.	Replace after shipment collection - Seller/shop entity has agreed to wait for the logistics team to collect the shipment from the buyer before replacing it)
2.	Refund after shipment collection - Seller/shop entity has agreed to wait for the logistics team to collect the shipment from the buyer before refunding)
3.	Refund without shipment collection - Seller/shop entity has agreed to refund the buyer without expecting the original shipment back)
4.	Replace without shipment collection - Seller/shop entity has agreed to replace the order without expecting the original shipment back)
5.	On certain select days as specified by Slrshoppee (such as 'The special offer Day') separate policies may be applicable.
In the event the Seller/shop entity accepts the return request raised by the Buyer, Buyer will have to return the product and then the refund shall be credited to the Buyers account.
In case the Seller/shop entity doesn't close the ticket in 3 days from the date of intimation to the Seller/shop entity about the refund request, the refund request shall be settled in favor of the Buyer.
Further for returns being made by Buyer to the Seller/shop entity of the product, the following parameters needs to be ensured by the Buyer:
Category	Condition
