Private communication, including email correspondence, is not regulated by Slrshoppee. Slrshoppee encourages its Users to be professional, courteous and respectful when communicating by email.
However, Slrshoppee will investigate and can take action on certain types of unwanted emails that violate Slrshoppee policies.
Such instances:
Threats of Bodily Harm - Slrshoppee does not permit Users to send explicit threats of bodily harm.
Misuse of Slrshoppee System - Slrshoppee allows Users to facilitate transactions through the Slrshoppee system, but will investigate any misuse of this service.
Spoof (Fake) email - Slrshoppee will never ask you to provide sensitive information through email. In case you receive any spoof (fake) email, you are requested to report the same to Us through 'Contact Us' tab.
Spam (Unsolicited Commercial email) - Slrshoppee's spam policy applies only to unsolicited commercial messages sent by Slrshoppee Users. Slrshoppee Users are not allowed to send spam messages to other Users.
Offers to Buy or Sell Outside of Slrshoppee - Slrshoppee prohibits email offers to buy or sell listed products outside of the Slrshoppee Platform. Offers of this nature are a potential fraud risk for both Buyers and Sellers/shop entity.
Slrshoppee policy prohibits user-to-user threats of physical harm via any method including, phone, email and on Our public message boards.
